
                        *********** GREEBLIES ***********

                                Written in Blitz 2

                                  BY ADAM GIRVIN

        The point of the game:

        Well, actually there isn't one. But that doesn't mean that
        it's crap. Basically, you must rid the galaxy of evil
        greeblies and kill the evil greeblie king before it  destroys
        the world!

        Copyright notice:

        This game is FREEWARE which means that it's free! (Well, you
(wouldn't expect to pay for this sort of thing). Feel free to copy it,
upload, download, give it to your mates, as long as you don't sell it
to make vast amounts of money or charge vast amounts of money to copy
it, nothing but a reasonable copying fee only!!!
        and yes, this game is copyright me, 1995. - Adam Girvin

Graphics & programming by me.
Music by Morph and Heatbeat of Rebels.

        if you wish to install this game to hard drive, be sure to copy
        ALL files into a greeblies drawer, for example and make an
        drawer called GREEBLIES and copy the lot. To load just click on
        greeblies.
